        Attributes that can be used with a PullToRefresh.

        AttributeDescription

        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrDrawableBottom
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrDrawableEnd Drawable to use as Loading Indicator in the Footer View.
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrDrawableStart Drawable to use as Loading Indicator in the Header View.
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrDrawableTop
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrHeaderBackground A drawable to use as the background of the Header and Footer Loading Views
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrHeaderSubTextColor Text Color of the Header and Footer Loading Views Sub Header
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrHeaderTextAppearance Base text color, typeface, size, and style for Header and Footer Loading Views
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrHeaderTextColor Text Color of the Header and Footer Loading Views
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrListViewExtrasEnabled Whether PullToRefreshListView has it's extras enabled.
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrMode Mode of Pull-to-Refresh that should be used
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrOverScroll Whether Android's built-in Over Scroll should be utilised for Pull-to-Refresh.
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrRefreshableViewBackground A drawable to use as the background of the Refreshable View
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrRotateDrawableWhilePulling Whether the Drawable should be continually rotated as you pull.
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrScrollingWhileRefreshingEnabled Whether the user can scroll while the View is Refreshing
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrShowIndicator Whether the Indicator overlay(s) should be used
        es.ugr.swad.swadroid:ptrSubHeaderTextAppearance Base text color, typeface, size, and style for Header and Footer Loading Views Sub Header
